  "prompt": "How can someone subscribe to Facebook topics on Quora?",
  "response": "To subscribe to Facebook topics on Quora, follow these steps:\n\n1. **Log In to Quora**: Make sure you are logged into your Quora account.\n\n2. **Search for Facebook Topics**: Use the search bar at the top of the page to type in \"Facebook\" or any specific topic related to Facebook that you are interested in.\n\n3. **Select the Topic**: Click on the topic you are interested in from the search results to go to the topic page.\n\n4. **Follow the Topic**: On the topic page, look for a \"Follow\" button. Clicking this will subscribe you to the topic, and you will start receiving updates and questions related to it in your feed.\n\n5. **Adjust Notifications**: If desired, you can adjust your notification settings to customize how you receive updates about the topics you follow.\n\nBy following these steps, you can stay updated on discussions and questions related to Facebook on Quora.",
